OL,3,C'Significant benefits for the South
OL,4,CWest': Andy Burnham on new defence plan
OL,6,FThe new Prime Minister has promised
OL,7,F"significant benefits" for the South
OL,8,FWest in the new defence investment
OL,9,Fplan.
OL,11,FIt comes as Andy Burnham has appointed
OL,12,FJohn Healey as one of the highest
OL,13,Fposts in government, Chancellor of the
OL,14,FExchequer.
OL,16,FUnder Keir Starmer, Healey served as
OL,17,FSecretary of State for Defence so he
OL,18,Fwill likely support increasing funding
OL,19,Ffor defence.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
