OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784729924
OL,3,C'Significant benefits for the South
OL,4,CWest': Andy Burnham on new defence plan
OL,6,FDuring his visit to Bath, The new
OL,7,FPrime Minister was asked if defence
OL,8,Fspending will be increased, which he
OL,9,Fdidn't rule out.
OL,11,F"We have put forward the defence
OL,12,Finvestment plan and it will have
OL,13,Fsignificant benefits for the south
OL,14,Fwest of England."
OL,16,FHe added: "I can confidently say to
OL,17,Fyou, it won't be too long before I'm
OL,18,Fback in this region showing how some
OL,19,Fof that investment from the defence
OL,20,Finvestment plan is going to benefit
OL,21,Fjobs in the South West of England."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784729924
OL,3,C'Significant benefits for the South
OL,4,CWest': Andy Burnham on new defence plan
OL,6,F"This is about Britain regaining its
OL,7,Freputation, for stability, for
OL,8,Fdelivering on what we say we will do
OL,9,Fand John Healy is extremely well
OL,10,Fplaced to do that."
OL,12,FThere has been concerns from local
OL,13,Fpoliticians that the South West will
OL,14,Fbe neglected with Andy Burnham having
OL,15,Fhuge ties to the north.
OL,17,FHowever he has defended his decision
OL,18,Fto only have one MP from the South
OL,19,FWest in his cabinet.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
