PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784729924
OL,3,C'Significant benefits for the South
OL,4,CWest': Andy Burnham on new defence plan
OL,6,FHeidi Alexander, MP for Swindon South
OL,7,Fretained her role as the Secretary of
OL,8,FState for Transport following the
OL,9,Freshuffle.
OL,11,FBurnham decided to remove Darren
OL,12,FJones, MP for Bristol North West who
OL,13,Fwas serving as Chancellor of the Duchy
OL,14,Fof Lancaster & Minister for the
OL,15,FCabinet Office and replaced him with
OL,16,FLouise Haigh, MP for Sheffield Heeley.
OL,18,FHe also served as Chief Secretary to
OL,19,Fthe Prime Minister. This role has now
OL,20,Fbeen abolished.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
