PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784729924
OL,3,C'Significant benefits for the South
OL,4,CWest': Andy Burnham on new defence plan
OL,6,FIn a post on social media Jones said
OL,7,F"It's been a privilege to be in the
OL,8,Fcabinet of a Labour government and to
OL,9,Fserve the country.
OL,11,F"Andy Burnham has called to tell me I
OL,12,Fwon't be a part of his new cabinet. I
OL,13,Fwish him and his team every success."
OL,15,FWhen asked why there is only one South
OL,16,FWest representative in his cabinet,
OL,17,FBurnham said: "It's not possible to
OL,18,Fevenly balance out every region within
OL,19,Fa cabinet.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
