PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784729924
OL,3,C'Significant benefits for the South
OL,4,CWest': Andy Burnham on new defence plan
OL,6,F"We have senior south west MP's in
OL,7,Fdifferent positions as well.
OL,9,F"Karin, Bristol MP continues as a
OL,10,Fminister of state in the department of
OL,11,Fhealth. Luke Pollard, minister of
OL,12,Fstate in defence. There are senior
OL,13,FSouth West representatives in the
OL,14,Fgovernment."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
